            <div id="answer1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="question1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                This system is designed to simplify the access to multiple services using a single set of credentials. Users register, receive ID cards, and provide fingerprints during registration. To access the system, users scan their ID cards and fingerprint, after which they can access various services seamlessly.
              </div>
            </div>
