            </h2>
            <div id="answer2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="question2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                With this system, you can access a range of services, including e-health, e-payment, e-voting, digital signatures, and e-banking, all using a single set of credentials.
